      right: ["Polyarticular flare involving multiple joints simultaneously","Visible tophaceous deposits on ears, hands, elbows, or Achilles tendons","Uric acid nephrolithiasis or urate nephropathy with declining renal function","Chronic joint destruction with 'rat-bite' erosions on X-ray","Refractory disease requiring pegloticase (failure of allopurinol and febuxostat)"]
